description: Yes, the game is Back! Another FNaF Fan Game Open Source Reuploaded, or ANFNAFFGOS Reuploaded for short is a reupload of the game Another FNaF Fan Game Open Source. I tried uploading it on Game Jolt, but the people over there went "nope" and deleted it.
